1. Dependencies
1.1 ffmpeg (http://tripp.arrozcru.org/)
1.2 JRuby >= 1.1.4
1.3 Rails 1.2.3
1.4 flvtool2 gem (gem install flvtool2)
1.5 activerecord-jdbcmysql-adapter 0.8.2
1.6 glassfish gem (gem install glassfish)
1.7 mysql

2. Deploy
2.0 setup the ffmpeg path and mp3 codec name in environment.rb
2.1 change config/database.yml
2.2 rake db:backup:dump (rake db:migrate)
2.3 rake testing
2.4 change config/war.rb
2.5 must be done after 2.2 testing!!! link upload-file-dir to the target
2.6 change the port in war_config.rb to 80
2.7 link mysql sock 
